---
// Premium Our Specialties Section - Swiss Trade Ventures
---

<section class="relative py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
        Our Specialties
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Swiss Trade Ventures Pvt Ltd stands at the forefront of global health equipment trading, 
        connecting healthcare providers worldwide with premium medical solutions and innovative technologies.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Simple Premium Core Values -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 lg:gap-20">
      
      <!-- Trust & Reliability -->
      <div class="text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background-color: #0003ff;">
